  4. [X] Deselect these packages (optional, leave them selected if you want installed):
     1. [X] ppp
     2. [X] reiserfsprogs
  5. [X] (Optionally) run 03-link-cache.sh as root
  6. [X] Edit /tmp/pacman.conf ( Add SigLevel=Never to options )
  7. [X] Install packages
  8. [X] Edit /etc/rc.conf [2/2]
     - [X] HOSTNAME=hostname
     - [X] DAEMONS=(syslog-ng !network crond sshd)
  9. [ ] (Optionally) run 04-stow-network-perl.sh as root
  10. [ ] (Optionally) run 05-copy-ssh-keys.sh as root
  11. [ ] (Optionally) run 06-pacman-cache.sh as root
